Project1-MultiSets version 1.0 07/17/2014  README file

TO COMPILE:
make -f makefile

GENERAL USAGE NOTES:
No special resources needed.
No configuration needed.


KNOW BUGS:
1. When the ingredient without quantity in the original cookbook file, the quantity will be input as 1 rather than empty.
2. When there is a section, and two recipes following the section, the program cannot read, and will exit.
3. When there is no quantity or unit in the ingredient, the output XML file still have a tag like <quantity></quantity><unit></unit> rather than not shown.


